  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libgweather</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libgweather</application> package is a library used
      to access weather information from online services for numerous
      locations.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          下载地址（HTTP）：<ulink url="&libgweather-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          下载地址（FTP）：<ulink url="&libgweather-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          MD5 校验和：&libgweather-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
